text: The separation of powers condifide in the U.S. Constitution does not permit Executive (Presidenital) interference in judicial matters. This is not normal. The Senate should be up in arms. The housing crisis is real. Tell everyone you know.  Changing HUD rules could make more affordable #housing available.   #gapol #vote Maya Dillard Smith #may19The Housing Authority of Savannah (HAS) will be accepting pre-applications for the Public Housing three (3) and four (4) four bedroom waiting lists only, for (3) days. The pre-applications will be accepted online ONLY at www.savannahpha.com from: • Wednesday, February 19, 2020, 8:00 a.m., through • Friday, February 21, 2020, 4:30 p.m. Not all households will be eligible for a three (3) or four (4) bedroom unit, as the age, gender and relationships of household members affect the number of bedrooms for which a household is eligible. Pre-applications may be submitted online from any computer, laptop or smartphone with internet access. Applicants may apply any time during the time period listed above. All pre-applications successfully submitted that qualify for a three (3) or four (4) bedroom unit will be taken. Placement on the waiting list will be determined by date and time of application and does not indicate that the family is, in fact, eligible for assistance. A final determination of eligibility will be made when the family is selected from the waiting lists. No pre- applications will be accepted before 8:00 a.m. Wednesday, February 19, 2020, or after 4:30 p.m. on Friday, February 21, 2020.

The DNC has changed its rules for participation in the Democratic primary debates, eliminating the individual donor requirement. This could allow Michael Bloomberg to participate in debates after the February 11 New Hampshire primary. So the rules were changed for Bloomberg, when they could have allowed more inclusivity before the candidates of color were forced out?  #TheMeansHaveToJustifyTheEnds #RulesShouldntBeBentForBillionaires https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-01-31/sanders-rivals-biden-for-top-spot-nationally-campaign-update?utm_medium=social&utm_campaign=socialflow-organic&utm_source=facebook&utm_content=business&cmpid=socialflow-facebook-business&fbclid=IwAR3frUQtfC0jrJbV_NuVTdY71Yfr6qfym-wYF30daocgUPB25MDR1u7NWH8
